  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106510/extras/44d511b98d93b5b8df21cd9041c66163.poster.avif?t=1764267905\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106510/extras/44d511b98d93b5b8df21cd9041c66163.webm?t=1764267905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106510/extras/44d511b98d93b5b8df21cd9041c66163.mp4?t=1764267905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In Floor 9, you find yourself trapped in a mysterious hotel known as \"Hotel Liminal.\" To escape, you must identify anomalies on each floor. These anomalies can be anywhere - on the ground, in paintings, or even right in front of your eyes. You must check every corner carefully, as one mistake will send you back to the beginning, to Floor 9. The game offers you a unique blend of eerie atmosphere, puzzle-solving, and survival, all wrapped up in a psychologically thrilling experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106510/extras/77d73c674a411add82c73f2651f5053b.poster.avif?t=1764267905\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106510/extras/77d73c674a411add82c73f2651f5053b.webm?t=1764267905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106510/extras/77d73c674a411add82c73f2651f5053b.mp4?t=1764267905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore a mysterious and atmospheric hotel setting<br></li><li>Discover intriguing anomalies on each floor<br></li><li>Engage in challenging gameplay that tests your observation and decision-making skills<br></li><li>Immerse yourself in eerie sound design</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106510/extras/44d511b98d93b5b8df21cd9041c66163.poster.avif?t=1764267905\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106510/extras/44d511b98d93b5b8df21cd9041c66163.webm?t=1764267905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106510/extras/44d511b98d93b5b8df21cd9041c66163.mp4?t=1764267905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In Floor 9, you find yourself trapped in a mysterious hotel known as \"Hotel Liminal.\" To escape, you must identify anomalies on each floor. These anomalies can be anywhere - on the ground, in paintings, or even right in front of your eyes. You must check every corner carefully, as one mistake will send you back to the beginning, to Floor 9. The game offers you a unique blend of eerie atmosphere, puzzle-solving, and survival, all wrapped up in a psychologically thrilling experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106510/extras/77d73c674a411add82c73f2651f5053b.poster.avif?t=1764267905\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106510/extras/77d73c674a411add82c73f2651f5053b.webm?t=1764267905\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106510/extras/77d73c674a411add82c73f2651f5053b.mp4?t=1764267905\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore a mysterious and atmospheric hotel setting<br></li><li>Discover intriguing anomalies on each floor<br></li><li>Engage in challenging gameplay that tests your observation and decision-making skills<br></li><li>Immerse yourself in eerie sound design</li></ul>",
